doctorList.education: Dr Deepika Das has a Bachelor of Homeopathic Medicine and Surgery degree from the National Homeopathic Medical College, Lucknow, along with a Bachelor of Science degree.
doctorList.aboutDr: Dr Deepika Das has been working as a Homoeopathic Consultant since 2015. She is also an Acting Homeopathic Consultant at Dr Batra’s Positive Health Clinic in Bhubaneswar. She has been practising homeopathy for the past two years.

doctorList.education: Dr Rohit Paul has a Bachelor of Homeopathic Medicine and Surgery degree from the National Homeopathic Medical College, Lucknow, along with a Bachelor of Science degree.
doctorList.aboutDr: Dr Rohit Paul has been working at Dr Batra’s™ for the past 12 years. From 2001 to 2003, she has worked as a Physician at Dr Mahesh Bhattacharya and Co. Kolkata, and, around the same time, she has also been an Honorary Physician at the Rotary club of Calcutta.

doctorList.education: Dr mahesh has a Bachelor of Homeopathic Medicine and Surgery degree from the National Homeopathic Medical College, Lucknow, along with a Bachelor of Science degree.
doctorList.aboutDr: Dr mahesh, Karnataka based classical homeopath with 13 years of clinical practice. Expertise in pediatric, skin disorders, & nutrition.  Postgraduate diploma and master degree in health education and clinical/therapeutic nutrition, life time member of Karnataka board of homeopathic system Bangalore.
